{"tid":742271,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"舊樓未炒盡地積比，有發展潛力所以50年樓齡仲有價有市，下一代大型屋苑炒盡地積比，逐漸進入40年，樓齡會唔會反映係樓價？","createTime":"2018-07-14T11:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T03:23:29.000Z","uid":12731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"25148d8f9763f89e67cc5dede2baad5264f32ef0","tid":742271,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"成日都諗唔明，依家啲舊樓咁上下舊就等人收購，所以就算高樓齡，維修保養費用貴都仲托得起樓價。但新少少果啲一早已經爆盡地積比，咁佢地越來越舊，發展商唔會收購，維修費又越來越貴？<br />\n<br />\n咁講法係咪傳統大型屋苑踏入40年樓齡都唔好再買，因為過多十幾廿年就無人問津，一路供仲要一路比俾天價維修費"},{"pid":"76598ff911edfb19822aa749fbd11c98b4807ad2","tid":742271,"uid":129340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"點會 港樓永遠唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a782dc4bfbe77c1c4f61273f49e9dbd2e1483d","tid":742271,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"有16層又係天橋隔離 下面又有商鋪 <br />\n雖然九龍近地鐵<br />\n但係咪唔駛諗重建"},{"pid":"d41be524e0df1d0a8ab2199cbbd98e382f1cc645","tid":742271,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港鐵站上蓋 車廠上蓋變危樓 港鐵咪又係要處理"},{"pid":"92d40faa925f576a5896a6f3938063dab34b9962","tid":742271,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"幾十年後改改個地積比"},{"pid":"f9437c71987455ae9377ccc39cc33ccea456c084","tid":742271,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71a782dc4bfbe77c1c4f61273f49e9dbd2e1483d","tid":742271,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"有16層又係天橋隔離 下面又有商鋪 <br />\n雖然九龍近地鐵<br />\n但係咪唔駛諗重建"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"講緊邊個樓盤？"},{"pid":"a674f0aaed0cc2825792327608396a503b230400","tid":742271,"uid":12731,"like":